{"id":2502,"date":"2023-06-06T08:44:33","date_gmt":"2023-06-06T01:44:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2502"},"modified":"2023-09-18T08:51:56","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T01:51:56","slug":"buoi-tap-huan-dao-tao-tu-xa-cua-giao-vien-can-bo-quan-ly-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/buoi-tap-huan-dao-tao-tu-xa-cua-giao-vien-can-bo-quan-ly-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do\/","title":{"rendered":"BU\u1ed4I T\u1eacP HU\u1ea4N \u0110\u00c0O T\u1ea0O T\u1eea XA C\u1ee6A GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN, C\u00c1N B\u1ed8 QU\u1ea2N L\u00dd TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ra \u0111\u1eddi nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t xu th\u1ebf t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 trong d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi, sau th\u1eddi gian t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c nhau, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1eadp trung nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n v\u1ec1 tri\u1ec3n khai tuy\u1ec3n sinh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb li\u00ean k\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ban n\u1eafm r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa, trang b\u1ecb ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa cho c\u00e1n b\u1ed9, gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean, chi\u1ec1u 2\/6 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tham d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n TS. Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00fay V\u00e2n, Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c; PGS. TS \u0110\u00e0o Th\u1ecb \u00c1i Thi, Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c Khoa chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n; c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c Gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean, C\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c khoa, ph\u00f2ng ban. T\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc li\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a qua c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, t\u1eeb h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng ty C\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_16016\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16016\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-16016 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Taphuan2-1024x578.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16016\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u00ean l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o h\u1ec7 t\u1eeb xa hi\u1ec7n nay. Trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Elearning bao g\u1ed3m di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n tin t\u1ee9c, ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01b0\u01a1ng chi ti\u1ebft, s\u00e1ch, gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, video c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, slide b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng, b\u00e0i t\u1eadp, ki\u1ec3m tra, c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd (xem l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc, xem \u0111i\u1ec3m thi v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p),\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n s\u1ed1 (cung c\u1ea5p gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh, s\u00e1ch, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o, c\u00e1c b\u00e0i b\u00e1o khoa h\u1ecdc ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u),\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng website (cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn sinh vi\u00ean nh\u01b0: tin t\u1ee9c, th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc, t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p,&#8230;),\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng tin nh\u1eafn SMS: th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi cho sinh vi\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Email: ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_16014\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16014\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-16014 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Taphuan1-1024x578.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16014\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi tr\u00ean trang qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nhi\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4 \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn cung c\u1ea5p h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ra \u0111\u1eddi nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t xu th\u1ebf t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i.\u00a0 Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 trong d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng h\u1ed9i [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2503,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[38],"tags":[41,53,42,40,45],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2502"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2502"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2502\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2505,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2502\/revisions\/2505"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2503"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2502"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2502"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2502"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}